## VLANs

| ID  | Name | Rules |
|:----|:------------|:---|
|   1 | Internal services | Internal services can access other VLANs |
|  10 | Public services | Blocked from accessing other things |
|  20 | Trusted | My desktop/laptop, access everything |
|  50 | Management | Can configure switches etc (not sure how that works?) |
| 100 | User devices | Access internal services + utilities + internet |
| 200 | IoT connected | Access only internet |
| 210 | IoT restricted | Access nothing |
| 220 | Utilities | Access only internet |
| 250 | Guest | Access internet + utilities |

